skills.Name: Eminent Attack Movement
skills.Description: Speed and P/M. Def. have a chance to increase every time you receive damage.

skills.Name: Air Light
skills.Description: For 30 minutes, you're less bound by gravity and P. Atk. + 10%.

skills.Name: Windy Healing Potion
skills.Description: Converts Windy Healing Potion. Elementary Alchemy.

skills.Name: Fluid Weave
skills.Description: For 3 seconds, P. Skill Evasion + 50%, P. Evasion + 50, M. Evasion + 50. Requires a fist weapon.

skills.Name: Alchemy Cube
skills.Description: Can use the Alchemy Cube. Elementary Combination Alchemy.

skills.Name: Eminent Stability
skills.Description: Max HP + 58, HP Recovery Bonus + 2.5, MP Recovery Bonus + 1.2.

skills.Name: Eminent Fist Weapon Mastery
skills.Description: When equipped with a fist weapon, P. Atk. + 10% and + 63, P. Accuracy + 3, Critical Rate + 10.

skills.Name: Eminent Light Armor Mastery
skills.Description: When equipped with light armor, P. Def. + 17, P. Evasion + 2, and the chance of receiving P./M. Critical Hit - 15%.

skills.Name: Eminent Ability
skills.Description: STR + 2.

skills.Name: Chin Strike
skills.Description: Knocks down target for 3 seconds. Requires a fist weapon.

skills.Name: Left Sidestep
skills.Description: Moves to the enemy's left and finds weakness. Cancels the opponent's target. Enemy is stunned for 5 seconds. Requires a fist weapon.

skills.Name: Lateral Hit
skills.Description: Attacks target with 22 Power added to P. Atk., and decreases P. Def. by 10% for 20 seconds. Till 20% more damage if target is stunned. Requires a fist weapon.

skills.Name: Backspin Blow
skills.Description: Attacks target with 129 Power added to P. Atk. Ignores 30% of target's P. Def. Requires a fist weapon.

skills.Name: Right Sidestep
skills.Description: Moves to the enemy's right and finds weakness. Cancels the opponent's target. Decreases enemy's resistance to fist weapons by  10% for 5 seconds. The decrease in resistance is not canceled when striking. Requires a fist weapon.
